<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-BR">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Atendimento - Muscle Way</title>
    <style>
      body {
        font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        background: #f4f6f9;
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
      }
      header {
        background: #1a1a1a;
        padding: 15px 30px;
        color: white;
        display: flex;
        justify-content: space-between;
        align-items: center;
      }
      header .logo {
        font-size: 22px;
        font-weight: bold;
        color: #3b82f6;
      }
      header nav a {
        margin-left: 20px;
        text-decoration: none;
        color: white;
        font-weight: bold;
        transition: 0.3s;
      }
      header nav a:hover {
        color: #3b82f6;
      }
      .container {
        max-width: 900px;
        margin: 40px auto;
        padding: 20px;
        background: white;
        border-radius: 12px;
        box-shadow: 0 0 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
      }
      h1 {
        text-align: center;
        color: #1a1a1a;
        margin-bottom: 20px;
      }
      p.subtitulo {
        text-align: center;
        color: #666;
        margin-bottom: 40px;
      }
      form {
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        gap: 20px;
      }
      label {
        font-weight: bold;
        margin-bottom: 5px;
        color: #333;
      }
      input,
      textarea {
        padding: 12px;
        border: 1px solid #ccc;
        border-radius: 8px;
        font-size: 15px;
        width: 100%;
      }
      textarea {
        resize: vertical;
        min-height: 120px;
      }
      button {
        padding: 14px;
        background: #3b82f6;
        color: white;
        font-size: 16px;
        font-weight: bold;
        border: none;
        border-radius: 8px;
        cursor: pointer;
        transition: 0.3s;
      }
      button:hover {
        background: #2563eb;
      }
      .info {
        margin-top: 40px;
        text-align: center;
        color: #555;
      }
      .info strong {
        display: block;
        margin-top: 8px;
        color: #1a1a1a;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <header>
      <div class="logo">MUSCLE WAY</div>
      <nav>
        <a href="/dashboard">InÃ­cio</a>
        <a href="/minhaconta">Minha Conta</a>
        <a href="/sair">Sair</a>
      </nav>
    </header>

    <div class="container">
      <h1>Atendimento ao Cliente</h1>
      <p class="subtitulo">
        Envie sua mensagem que nossa equipe entrarÃ¡ em contato!
      </p>
      <form action="/atendimento" method="POST">
        <div>
          <label for="nome">Nome</label>
          <input
            type="text"
            id="nome"
            name="nome"
            placeholder="Digite seu nome"
            required
          />
        </div>
        <div>
          <label for="email">E-mail</label>
          <input
            type="email"
            id="email"
            name="email"
            placeholder="Digite seu e-mail"
            required
          />
        </div>
        <div>
          <label for="mensagem">Mensagem</label>
          <textarea
            id="mensagem"
            name="mensagem"
            placeholder="Escreva sua mensagem..."
            required
          ></textarea>
        </div>

        <button type="submit">Enviar</button>
      </form>
      <div class="info">
        <p>Ou se preferir, fale com a gente pelo WhatsApp:</p>
